headline: Opinion: It's Time to Buy UnitedHealth Group Stock After a 50% Plunge
summary: Most of UnitedHealth Group's issues should be temporary.  The price is right to buy UnitedHealth Group stock after its steep decline.  UnitedHealth Group (NYSE: UNH) might want to change its stock ticker from "UNH" to "UGH."
